An Ingress controller is a specialized load balancer for Kubernetes (and other containerized) environments. 
Kubernetes is the de facto standard for managing containerized applications.

Egress :
the data egress describes yhe outbound traffic originating with in a network.

Ingress : 
Traffic that originates outside the network that travelling ointo yhe network.


Physical Layer.
Data Link Layer. 
Network Layer.  tcp and udp 
Transport Layer. 
Session Layer.
Presentation Layer. 
Application Layer. http -80 https -443
